                  <persName id="t18240715-98-person892">
                  DAVID 
                  DOOLEY
               <interp inst="t18240715-98-person892" type="surname" value="DOOLEY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240715-98-person892" type="given" value="DAVID"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240715-98-person892" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a carpenter. On the 12th July I was working at a building in Wardour-street. I found the prisoner there at four o'clock in the morning, and asked his business at that nseasonable hour; he said he had come to sleep there - I searched him and found this lead on his person - he asked me to let him go - I gave in charge - the lead had been cut from the gutters - I compared it, it fitted exactly - I found a knife on him which appeared to have cut lead.</p>
